pe":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"typearg\"><em>typeArg</em></dt>\n <dd>イベントの名前を表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"compositioneventinit\"><em>CompositionEventInit</em><span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dd><code>CompositionEventInit</code> 辞書オブジェクトは、次のメンバーを含むことができます:\n\n <ul>\n  <li><code>data</code>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CompositionEvent\"><code>CompositionEvent</code></a> オブジェクトの <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CompositionEvent/data\"><code>data</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 属性を IME コンポジションにより生成された文字に初期化します。</li>\n </ul>\n\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n <p><strong>補足</strong>: <code>CompositionEventInit</code> 辞書は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/UIEvent/UIEvent\" title=\"UIEventInit\"><code>UIEventInit</code></a> 辞書から継承するため、そこで定義されたメンバーも受け入れます。</p>\n </div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">策定状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2014/WD-DOM-Level-3-Events-20140925/#dom-compositionevent-compositionevent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 3 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">CompositionEvent() の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザー実装状況","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CompositionEvent.CompositionEvent","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/CompositionEvent/CompositionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":